guRa :: sAmAnyakARqaH guRa puM upasarjana klI upAgrya klI apraDAna klI guRopasarjanopAgryARyapraDAne'DamaM punaH            nikfzwamaRakaM garhyamavadyaM kARqakutsite   apakfzwaM pratikfzwaM yApyaM rePo'vamaM bruvam            KewaM pApamapaSadaM kupUyaM celamarva ca
